snippet.title: LumbearJack Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Grab your axe and save the environment by chopping and recycling every man-made thing in your path! Solve physics-based environmental puzzles to show the destructive Evil Works who’s boss. 
🎤 Discord: https://discord.gg/8sgszsE63y
🔗 Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1582290/LumbearJack/
🔗 Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/lumbearjack


Jack is a humble Lumbearjack with a simple dream: to return to nature what is hers with the help of his trusty ax and his animal friends. Through real-time physics puzzles, fight destruction with destruction to thwart the sinister plans of up-and-coming industrial giant Evil Works.
